Included Medicine
The new version of Sisoft Sandra allows us to obtain the performance of various devices such as your computer's processor, memory or hard drives, and compared with that obtained by other teams.

Sisoft Sandra also shows information about the configuration of system software such as information on DirectX, memory usage or operating system.

This new version of Sisoft Sandra comes with a new interface more attractive and intuitive, new testing options and information on the efficiency of power management, memory latency, the speed of hard drives and CD and DVD and updating some of the tests already included in previous versions.

Includes versions

* Sandra Professional Home
* Sandra Engineer Standard
* Sandra Enterprise
* Sandra Professional Business
